attributionInfo.brokerName: Century 21 Hometown Realty, Arroyo Grande Office

data.description: Nestled on a spacious 1.15-acre lot, this property presents an exciting opportunity for those seeking to craft their dream home in Arroyo Grande. Boasting a 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2,014 sq ft house, this residence offers comfortable living and the potential to create something extraordinary. Step inside to discover a welcoming interior, with a two-car garage that includes a bonus room, accessible from the backside of the garage. This additional space provides versatility for a home office, studio, or guest suite. Outside, your imagination can run wild on this expansive lot, which features a shop and ample room for upgrades and outdoor projects. The property offers flexibility with a septic tank, solar panel lease, a well, and access to public water. While the owners have exclusively used the well for their water supply, the availability of public water opens up endless possibilities. 2730 Southview Ave is more than a home; it's a canvas for your vision. Imagine lush gardens, a swimming pool, or even a mini orchard - your dream property awaits.
